                     <interp inst="t17850112-53-off282" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17850112-53-off282" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17850112-53-cd283" type="crimeDate">9th of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17850112-53-off282 t17850112-53-cd283"></join>, two linen shirts, value 2 s. two caps, value 2 d. two pair of cotton stockings, value 1 s. one pair of thread stockings, value 6 d. one table cloth, value 2 d. one apron, value 6 d. oue pocket-book, value 2 d. and one silk purse, value 3 d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17850112-53-victim638" type="victimName">
                     Jonathan 
                     Bradley
                  <interp inst="t17850112-53-victim638" type="surname" value="Bradley"></interp>
